    .about-us#about
      .about-us__wrapper

        .about-us__content
          h2.about-us__headline What is Climate&nbsp;Mind?
          .about-us__subline A tool to relate everyone and their lives to the effects of climate change.
          .about-us__text We created a web app that helps users explore how their values and personal interests are being affected by climate change.
          .about-us__text We aim to inspire users to take action with a range of attractive solutions consistent with their values that they can get excited about.
          .about-us__text We are past the early stages of development and could use a few more hands to scale-up our progress.

        .about-us__teaser
          img.about-us__icon(src="images/what-is-climateMind.svg")
          .about-us__slogan We want to make constructive conversations about climate change easier.
            
    .insights
      .insights__wrapper
        h2.insights__headline How does it work?
        .insights__content
          .insights__subline Climate Mind consists of a web application and a knowledge base.
          .insights__text The web and mobile applications guide users through the process of personalizing climate conversations with others and responding to common climate change myths. Then it provides achievable action proposals that align with the values and interests of the user.
          .insights__text The knowledge base collects knowledge available on climate change and interpret it as sets of concepts and the relationships between them.
          a.button(href="https://app.climatemind.org/" target="_blank") Go to the Web App
      .insights__wrapper
        a(href="https://app.climatemind.org/" target="_blank")
